### Variables
@baseUrl = https://localhost:7212
@apiBase = {{baseUrl}}/api

### Get all active downloads
GET {{apiBase}}/downloads
Accept: application/json

### Get download status for a specific model
GET {{apiBase}}/downloads/hf:bartowski/Llama-3.2-3B-Instruct-GGUF/Llama-3.2-3B-Instruct-IQ3_M/status
Accept: application/json

### Start downloading a model
POST {{apiBase}}/downloads/hf:bartowski/Llama-3.2-3B-Instruct-GGUF/Llama-3.2-3B-Instruct-IQ3_M
Accept: application/json

### Pause download
POST {{apiBase}}/downloads/hf:bartowski/Llama-3.2-3B-Instruct-GGUF/Llama-3.2-3B-Instruct-IQ3_M/pause
Accept: application/json

### Resume download
POST {{apiBase}}/downloads/hf:bartowski/Llama-3.2-3B-Instruct-GGUF/Llama-3.2-3B-Instruct-IQ3_M/resume
Accept: application/json

### Cancel download
POST {{apiBase}}/downloads/hf:bartowski/Llama-3.2-3B-Instruct-GGUF/Llama-3.2-3B-Instruct-IQ3_M/cancel
Accept: application/json

### Get model info without downloading
GET {{apiBase}}/downloads/hf:bartowski/Llama-3.2-3B-Instruct-GGUF/Llama-3.2-3B-Instruct-IQ3_M/info
Accept: application/json

### Get repository info
GET {{apiBase}}/downloads/repository/bartowski/Llama-3.2-3B-Instruct-GGUF
Accept: application/json